text: Eunidia fuscovitticollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1958.BioLib.cz - Eunidia fuscovitticollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1958
